name: libmkfs_msdos
desc:
This library comes from the `newfs_msdos` utility, which is installed by default in the aquaBSD core base. You can find it at `sbin/newfs_msdos/mkfs_msdos.*`.
A manpage is coming soon!
This library will probably be integrated into base at some point.

WWW: https://github.com/inobulles/iar
